<p>THINK of others - be <u>considerate</u>. <p>Don't<u> play</u> with that SWORD.<p>

Your <u>epidermis</u> is in the tiger's STOMACH. <p>
 The HEDGEHOG is inside an <u>empty</u> tiger.</p>

